Comment: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:00.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,出现钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:10.04,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Fate doom and future　dark over light
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:13.26,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:15.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:18.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:20.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:25.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,錆びついた　shadow prison　姿潜めて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:30.48,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,行き場を探しては　I keep my soul in you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:33.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:35.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Never give up that fight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:37.82,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:40.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Don't let it claim your light rise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:45.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,果てなきを彷徨う　飽く無き声が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:50.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,足枷を解いて　羽ばたくの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:53.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,時間の狭間で召されてく魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.47,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,たとえ全てを焼き尽くされたとし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:04:00.14,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,ても　飲み込んで　しまえば
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:05.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇を振り翳して　胸に宿すアンサー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1370,27)}闇中反転　照らして
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:10.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&\3a&HFF&\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1365.333,91.001)}Aren't you? 明鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:10.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FF&\3c&H0000FF&\3a&HFF&\pos(1370.666,35)}Won't you make yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:10.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1720,74.668)} -> 探すの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:12.23,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,君を守りたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.86,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,そのに呼びかけるから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:19.82,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇中宣戦　全身全霊　生きてゆく証
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:19.82,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fs31\pos(1184,80)\bord1.2}climb back up unswayed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:22.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru(get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:24.79,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:27.04,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru(get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:30.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru get out
